```scss
@mixin line-clamp-2 {
  overflow: hidden;
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  line-clamp: 2;
}

.box {
  @include line-clamp-2;
  
  height: 100%;
  width: 100%;
}
```